- Test: Admin creates user with weak password (too short, no uppercase, no digit) → 422 with password violation messages.
- Test: Admin resets password to weak password → 422.
- Test: Non-admin tries to create user → 403.

---

## Execution Order

1. **Policy fixes** (B1a→B1f, B2b, B3) — pure class changes, no new files
2. **Controller auth fixes** (B1d, B1f, B2a) — call policy methods
3. **Canary server-side fix** (H4a→H4c) — remove client trust, compute from DB/config
4. **Outbound linkage fix** (H5) — add workflow approval guard in service
5. **Multi-file attachment** (H6a→H6b) — change request + controller
6. **Metrics instrumentation** (M7a→M7f) — new middleware + job, inject service, schedule
7. **Password enforcement** (M8a→M8d) — new controller + requests + routes
8. **All test updates** (T1→T8) — update existing + add new tests

---

## Verification Checklist (Static Re-Audit)

| Finding | Evidence After Fix |
|---|---|
| DocumentPolicy.archive dept scope | `DocumentPolicy.php:archive` includes `inSameDepartment || hasCrossScope` |
| SalesDocumentPolicy.update dept scope | `SalesDocumentPolicy.php:update` includes dept check |
| SalesDocument complete/linkOutbound use policy | Controller calls `authorize('complete'/'linkOutbound', $document)` |
| ReturnController update/complete use policy | Controller calls `authorize('update'/'complete', $return)` |
| Attachment upload scopes parent record | `AttachmentController::store` loads record + calls `authorize('view', $record)` |
| Attachment delete dept scope | `AttachmentPolicy::delete` checks dept_id |
| Workflow node show instance-level | `WorkflowNodeController::show` calls `authorize('view', $node->instance)` |
| Canary cap from server | Request has no `eligible_count`; controller computes from DB/config |
| Outbound linkage workflow gate | `SalesDocumentService::linkOutbound` checks workflow status |
| Multi-file attachment | Request accepts `files[]`; controller loops and returns array |
| Metrics produced in app flows | Middleware records request_timing; WorkflowService records failed_approvals; Job records queue_depth |
| PasswordPolicy enforced | AdminUserController form requests call `PasswordPolicy::violations()` |
| Test coverage gaps | Cross-dept 403 tests added; canary tamper test; node show unrelated user 403; return scope 403; metrics producer tests; password rejection tests |
"}

