   **Request 2 (new instruction):** After the user provided `audit_report_1_fix-check_round1.md`, address the one remaining "Partially Fixed" finding: Issue 5 (High) — outbound linkage still allowed on completed sales documents with no linked workflow instance. Fix surgically without touching unrelated/already-fixed code.

2. Key Technical Concepts:
   - Laravel 11 DDD architecture (Domain/Application/Infrastructure layers)
