     ```

   - **`app/Application/Sales/SalesDocumentService.php`** — Issue 5 final fix
     - Removed the conditional `if ($doc->workflow_instance_id !== null)` guard, making the workflow approval check unconditional. Updated docblock to remove "if a workflow instance is linked" language.
     ```php
     // BEFORE:
     // Documents without a linked workflow may proceed on Completed status alone.
     if ($doc->workflow_instance_id !== null) {
         $doc->loadMissing('workflowInstance');
         if ($doc->workflowInstance === null
             || $doc->workflowInstance->status !== \App\Domain\Workflow\Enums\WorkflowStatus::Approved) {
