# Plan: Audit Remediation Round 2 — Full PASS on All Findings (audit_report-2.md)

## Context

`audit_report-2.md` identified 2 Blockers, 4 High, and 2 Medium severity findings across API completeness, workflow integrity, attachment security, backup security/retention, and an API contract inconsistency. This plan surgically addresses every finding in the exact files cited in the report evidence, plus the minimum necessary test additions to achieve full static coverage.

Goal: after these changes, every audit category re-runs as **PASS**.

---

## Critical Files Inventory

| Finding | File(s) Affected |
|---|---|
| BLOCKER-1 | New `app/Http/Controllers/Api/RoleController.php` + `DepartmentController.php`; `routes/api.php:44,46` already wired |
